---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Our Story | YourHQ - Infrastructure + Warmth" 
  description="Founded by Lian and Penny in Whangārei. We combine high-tech infrastructure with Pacific warmth."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-paper min-h-screen">
    
    <!-- HEADER -->
    <section class="pt-32 pb-24 border-b border-carbon bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="text-6xl md:text-8xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter leading-[0.9] mb-12">
            Infrastructure <br/>
            <span class="text-frangipani">& Warmth.</span>
        </h1>
        <div class="max-w-2xl border-l-4 border-carbon pl-8 py-2">
            <p class="text-2xl font-medium leading-relaxed">
                We bridge the gap between Silicon Valley tech and Pacific hospitality. Between code and conversation.
            </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

   <!-- THE ORIGIN -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-paper border-b border-carbon overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
                
     <!-- ... inside the grid ... -->

<!-- LEFT SIDE -->
<div class="md:col-span-5">
    <h2 class="text-xs font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-400 mb-8">The 15-Year Timeline</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="transform -rotate-2 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-1.png" alt="Lian and Penny" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div class="transform rotate-2 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-5.png" alt="Whangarei" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div class="transform rotate-1 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-3.png" alt="Dinner and ideas" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
        <div class="transform -rotate-1 border-4 border-white shadow-hard aspect-square overflow-hidden">
            <img src="/us-4.png" alt="Early days" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- RIGHT SIDE -->
<div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-8 text-lg text-carbon/80 leading-relaxed pt-8">
    <div class="md:hidden mb-8">
        <!-- Mobile-only image -->
        <img src="/us-3.png" class="w-full border-2 border-carbon shadow-hard" alt="Lian and Penny" />
    </div>

    <p>
        Lian and Penny have known each other for 15 years. We've always bonded over a shared passion: <strong>Storytelling</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
        Recently, over coffee in Whangārei, we realized something troubling. So many of the local businesses we loved were digitally homeless. The builders, the bakers, the tradies who've been around for 20 years.
    </p>
    <p>
        They were living entirely on Facebook or Instagram — vulnerable to algorithms they couldn't control.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-white p-8 border border-carbon my-8 shadow-hard-sm relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-24 h-6 bg-frangipani/80 rotate-1"></div>
        <p class="font-bold text-xl text-carbon mb-2">We thought: This isn't right.</p>
        <p>It's time for business owners to stop being tenants and start being owners.</p>
    </div>

    <p>
        So we decided to build something about it.
    </p>
</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE TEAM -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-white border-b border-carbon">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
                
                <!-- Lian -->
                <div>
                    <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon mb-8 relative overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="/lian-headshot.png" alt="Lian Passmore" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">Lian</h3>
                    <p class="font-mono text-sm text-signal font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">The Architect</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        Lian brings the tech. With a background in automation and AI, she ensures the "factory" runs with precision.
                    </p>

                    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">Lian's Story:</p>
                            <p>Grew up watching her dad run a small business — brilliant at the work, frustrated by the admin. She married someone in the trades. Same story. While studying technological futures and data sovereignty, she kept thinking: <em>Why aren't we building tools for people like my dad? Like my husband?</em> That became her mission: <strong>Use cutting-edge tech to empower everyday business owners.</strong></p>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">What Lian Believes:</p>
                            <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                <li>• Strong infrastructure is the highest form of care</li>
                                <li>• Technology should empower, not confuse</li>
                                <li>• Small businesses deserve Silicon Valley tools</li>
                                <li>• If it can be automated, it should be</li>
                                <li>• You should own your digital space, not rent it</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">Background:</p>
                            <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                <li>• Studied technological futures & data sovereignty</li>
                                <li>• Deep passion for SMEs (grew up around small business)</li>
                                <li>• Builds AI agents & automation systems</li>
                                <li>• Uses Astro + Tailwind CSS for high-performance sites</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-2">
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon">Lian's Specialty:</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">AI voice agents (the Digital Twin), automation systems, and Silicon Valley infrastructure with real-world empathy.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Penny -->
                <div>
                    <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-gray-100 border border-carbon mb-8 relative overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="/penny-headshot.png" alt="Penny" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-2">Penny</h3>
                    <p class="font-mono text-sm text-hibiscus font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">The Heart</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                        Penny brings the warmth. She builds the relationships and ensures every client feels heard, understood, and looked after.
                    </p>

                    <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">Penny's Story:</p>
                            <p>Lives in Whangārei raising her daughter. Watching her daughter explore the world with curiosity reminded Penny to be bold, embrace creativity, and see things with fresh eyes. She rediscovered her courage to ask: <em>What brings me joy?</em> The answer: <strong>Helping people.</strong></p>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">What Penny Believes:</p>
                            <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                <li>• Every business has a story worth telling</li>
                                <li>• People want to be understood, not sold to</li>
                                <li>• Technology should make life easier, not harder</li>
                                <li>• Good design feels like the person behind it</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon mb-2">Background:</p>
                            <ul class="space-y-1 text-xs text-gray-500">
                                <li>• 15+ years in customer support & project administration</li>
                                <li>• Cook Island & Pacific heritage</li>
                                <li>• Built AI solutions (Awhina AI) for real-time service</li>
                                <li>• Natural connector who makes people feel at ease</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                        <div class="pt-2">
                            <p class="font-bold text-carbon">Penny's Specialty:</p>
                            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">Making your website feel authentically like <em>you</em>, and giving you time back (not taking more of it).</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PACIFIC ROOTS -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-carbon text-paper">
        <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8">Born from the Pacific.</h2>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-12">
                    Like many Pacific people raised in Aotearoa, we grew up disconnected from our heritage languages but deeply connected to the values: <strong>Service, Respect, and Stewardship.</strong>
                </p>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                    <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <strong class="block text-frangipani mb-2 text-lg">Ownership</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">You own the house. No landlords.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <strong class="block text-hibiscus mb-2 text-lg">Stewardship</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">We care for it, but we don't hold it hostage.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border border-gray-700 p-6">
                        <strong class="block text-signal mb-2 text-lg">Respect</strong>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Tech should serve you, not confuse you.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-base text-gray-300 mt-12 font-medium">
                    These aren't borrowed concepts. They're how we were raised to do business.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>